snippet.title: Steam Heroes Xbox Indie Game Trailer
snippet.description: A new puzzle strategy game developed by Tiamat Games and ProjectorGames for the Xbox 360.  Due for release late September 2010, this game combines strategy & skill to overcome the minions of the evil Baron Von Smog.  Includes 12 action-packed stages, a full soundtrack, competitive online play and an advanced mode for expert gamers.  Visit www.tiamatgames.com/steamheroes.htm for more information.
